{"updated_at": "2011-11-15T21:23:55Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2011-11-15T21:23:38Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2751552", "id": 2751552, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/1993", "issue_id": 1993, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/softwaregravy", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "a88bec2f50dd9f21cd282432cb9e7a92", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a88bec2f50dd9f21cd282432cb9e7a92?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F4c9b5a6919028b0fbe0601f9428681d5.png", "id": 426690, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/events{/privacy}", "login": "softwaregravy", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/softwaregravy/followers"}, "body": "The current situation is not much different, and, I'd argue, probably worse.  You currently can't remove, rename, or 'alter' impacted sequences -- it's a one way migration, and one you might not catch until it already goes to prod.\r\n\r\nIf you've already migrated a migration with this issue, the only way to fix it is to manually log into the database to manually undo the index then remove/change the migration(file) that added the 'too long index' (and then do you remove the migration from the rollback sequence?).  \r\n\r\nWith the fix, theoretically, this should be raised in a development database migration without messing up prod.    ", "_id": {"$oid": "523fe6c0bd354364b901c1c3"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1993#issuecomment-2751552"}
